movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Good vs. Evil On a Grand Scale
review: If you want action, it's got it, if you want adventure it's got that too. It's the Background we need, the history we missed.And yes, it's another grand epic of Good vs Evil,..It is loaded with special effects, and memorable dialogue, andThe immortal tagline, 'I've got a bad feeling about this'I say, check it out ,...
